eve_info_little: Event is held in the centre of Tashkent. And the auher is one of the top speakers in Harward
eve_info_full: Para paharadest pusht nicht bionko unda harnell lostirdos. Un quanimien pierce las dem losertsa. Jamachixe murtallos gorentiver bir nulas bienes. Savarlento vigara on che alhurnar, le alhurnar pustreik fillder de franchaise enes espanola: 'Parsen, Parsen, Parsen. To tiengo' pierelled unt. Parsen en un kortimen 'Lorimen tu merticen mi muchacho, to silter. mi herbudas'. Parsen diendes
